Name: Bunny Girl Story
About the game: The girl works in the Bunny Club. She loves to sing songs and dance. But she is alone. However one day there is an opportunity to change everything. In the game, your goal is to collect the puzzle in order to restore the pictures to learn the whole story with our Bunny Girl.
